PrecisReappointment of KEVIN D’SOUZA of Langley, British Columbia, as a full-time member of the Pacific Regional Division of the Parole Board of Canada, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of five years; and his designation as Vice-Chairperson of the Pacific Regional Division of the Parole Board of Canada, effective June 20, 2022.
